{"tid":2495285,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"11.2灣仔武器庫案 5人被控串謀縱火已被還押17個月  1人今承認交替控罪管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪 4月30日判刑","createTime":"2021-04-19T05:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T17:22:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"61797f24ec67b56db75ef2699d73bbfcd0577ddf","tid":2495285,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:43:35.000Z","msg":"警方於前年11月，搗破灣仔冠景樓一個臨時武器庫，檢獲逾百支製成或半製成汽油彈、伸縮警棍、胡椒噴霧、防毒面罩等物品，懷疑用於同日在港島的示威。四男一女被拘控串謀縱火罪，女被告今在區域法院承認交換控罪中的管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪，案件押後至4月30日下午判刑，期間被告繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n23歲被告被控於2019年11月2日，當警務人員破門進入灣仔堅拿道西10號冠景樓4樓F室的處所期間，在該處保管59個汽油彈，79個玻璃瓶每個載有白色廢棉、50個玻璃樽、約4.6公升含柴油液體、約1公斤含異丙醇液體、約4.9公斤含汽油液體、白色廢棉、布條、布及毛巾，意圖在無合理辯解的情況下用以摧毀或損壞屬於另一人的財產。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，一名人士在前年10月31日至11月4日，透過Airbnb 租用涉案單位，為期5天4夜。就在11月2日，即維園舉行集會當天，警方刑事情報科人員就單位進行監視行動，同日下午3時決定採取行動。兩名警員掩至單位門外，察覺有濃烈汽油味傳出，其中一名警員表露身分並要求單位內人士開門，唯不獲回應，遂展破門行動。<br />\n<br />\n逗留在大樓外觀察的警員發現，單位內的4男1女走到露台位置，跳至3樓簷蓬再跳至3樓平台，並遭一名不知名人士拍下過程。片段中5人均沒有蒙面，面容清晰可見。<br />\n<br />\n一名俄羅斯籍男子當時身處3A室，他目睹並透過片段確認，上述5人是從3A室的露台外衝入其單位內，他們當中有人受傷，並曾要求留在其單位內，但俄籍男子拒絕並要求他們離開，5人最終從單位正門離去。<br />\n<br />\n同日3時許，兩名警員發現楊與另一被告躲在2樓電梯大堂近防煙門的一幅活動木板後，於是將他們控制。其他警員及後亦在2樓男洗手間及一間餐廳內，發現其他被告，各人被捕後在警誡下保持緘默。"},{"pid":"778bb0359ff127213a6c2739240280f2c8589f84","tid":2495285,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79095153ce3fce12590dfab53e81080fb28c4bf9","tid":2495285,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4977d95debd84ffcf297c7b68f4e483c83ddff","tid":2495285,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"四年得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dd3567e9bdd88f9bcb4ec3063bb441dff1c72c","tid":2495285,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71142e3310319a0a4564a58b3ee2a16984ae2e62","tid":2495285,"uid":22341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a463c6a495480dbcb6f305ccadfe549a1e09d5b","tid":2495285,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"446761bc04b43cc5bd86f4f8429779e5c04858c3","tid":2495285,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"一個認. 4個唔認.<br />\n<br />\nGG"},{"pid":"c2e16ed2e6a7197f6fe242f184fd32cece7399d2","tid":2495285,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"五名年青男女被指前年 11 月初，在灣仔管有 138 支懷疑汽油彈，遭控串謀縱火罪，以及一項交替的管有物品意圖損壞他人財產罪，五人還押至今逾一年半。其中一名被告，今（19 日)在區域法院承認一項管有物品意圖損壞他人財產罪，案件押後至 4 月 30 日求情和判刑，其間須繼續還押。根據控方案情，警方破門時，五男女曾經從露台跳至下層簷蓬，再從薝蓬跳至平台離開，其後在不同地點被捕。<br />\n<br />\n女被告應訊前，在被告欄向公眾席揮手，做心型手勢，即使佩戴口罩亦難掩燦爛笑容。當控方完成案情後，法官問被告是否明白及同意案情時，被告表示「非常詳盡」、「同意」。法官葉佐文及後主動問及辯方關於被告的健康，辯方表示被告的健康正常，無問題。<br />\n<br />\n就被告承認的一項管有物品意圖損壞他人財產罪，案情指，前年 10 月 31 日至 11 月 4 日，有人透過Airbnb 租用涉案單位。11 月 2 日，警方刑事情報科人員，對單位進行監視行動。當中觀察人員 SO5 和 SO6 在大樓外觀察，留意單位面向軒尼詩道和寶靈頓道露台的情況，而行動組人員 SO1 至 SO4 則在大樓附近一帶候命。<br />\n<br />\n同日約下午3 時，警方決定採取行動，SO1 至 SO4 在單位門外察覺有濃烈氣油味從單位內傳出。此時，SO1 表露警員身份，要求單位內人士開門，惟無人回應， SO1 至 SO4 隨即破門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A-%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E8%97%8F%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B3-4-%E6%9C%88-30-%E6%97%A5%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258D%258A-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%2587%25B3-4-%25E6%259C%2588-30-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=565791d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258D%258A-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%2587%25B3-4-%25E6%259C%2588-30-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=ba8dbc3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A-%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E8%97%8F%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B3-4-%E6%9C%88-30-%E6%97%A5%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/</a>"},{"pid":"6ae6d30ccc8b30b7d4eb2c2abe0112fdf4363a42","tid":2495285,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f924d8c74aef2475bb5354f87013940a672923","tid":2495285,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc4977d95debd84ffcf297c7b68f4e483c83ddff","tid":2495285,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"四年得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"量刑起點料約4年<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時希望法官今日判刑，因未知上訴庭之後會否頒下其他指引，擔心影響被告刑罰。辯方指被告對事件感到後悔，獲家人支持。辯方呈上案例，稱明白量刑起點應不少於45個月，但認為不至於判囚4至5年。法官押後判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/QM4GAQPEEBAXLLJIVTCFOERBBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2FQM4GAQPEEBAXLLJIVTCFOERBBQ%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=c0306a85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2FQM4GAQPEEBAXLLJIVTCFOERBBQ%2F&h=109d1ca5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/QM4GAQPEEBAXLLJIVTCFOERBBQ/</a>"},{"pid":"6616d0c9eb090f3ae8ba1e40a8a27d43889dc50e","tid":2495285,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1532582d8834efb3e76cfd3d4d2a9e701f33ae4c","tid":2495285,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:15:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d3a88b2d94468ac3748a0138effecb953629ac6","tid":2495285,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83f472796408b8ff53f23c95b71fe554d426bde","tid":2495285,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317b3deaf64bf646f482e770cb59bc42e8d12a46","tid":2495285,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"原來咁驚險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09a9d85f2807a31432a6bce5ea2283b1c641b23","tid":2495285,"uid":75583,"like"